<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="waterzone">
      <h1 class="you">ðŸ”– Personal Bookmark Manager</h1>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/bookmark/add">Add Bookmark</a></li>
        <li><a href="/bookmark/list">Bookmark List</a></li>
        <% if (email) { %>
          <li>
            <form action="/logout" style="display:inline;">
              <button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
            </form>
          </li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Welcome to Your Personal Bookmark Manager</h1>
    <p>
      This web app helps you save, organize, and access your favorite URLs quickly and easily.
      Keep your important links in one place, searchable and manageable with editing capabilities.
      Sign up now to start building your personalized collection of bookmarks.
    </p>

    <section class="featured">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
          <h3>Easy Bookmarking</h3>
          <p>Add URLs with titles to keep track of websites you love or need to revisit.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Organize & Search</h3>
          <p>View your bookmarks in a paginated list with a search option to quickly find titles or URLs.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Edit & Manage</h3>
          <p>Modify or delete bookmarks whenever you want. Keep your collection up to date.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
      <h2>Why Use a Bookmark Manager?</h2>
      <p>Stop losing important links in browser clutter or forgetting useful resources.
      A personal bookmark manager keeps everything neat, accessible, and under your control.</p>
      <p>Join today and experience hassle-free web browsing by saving your favorite sites with ease!</p>
    </section>
  </main>
